## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:machinelearningservices:DataVersion 1 /subscriptions/00000000-1111-2222-3333-444444444444/resourceGroups/testrg123/providers/Microsoft.MachineLearningServices/workspaces/testworkspace/data/dataset123/versions/1 
```
